summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the laying off, opening, widening and establishing of Northeast 125th Street, . . . Roosevelt Way Northeast, . . . the east side of 5th Avenue Northeast, . . . 17th Avenue Northeast, . . . 25th Avenue Northeast, . . . all at existing center line grade; providing for the condemnation, . . . of land and other property necessary therefor; providing for . . . slopes . . . ; providing for the condemnation, . . . for retaining wall and storm drainage purposes; providing for . . . temporary construction easements, and providing for payment therefor.
